Setup was done in VMware, and created the LAN segments. 

Ubuntu Server 

	• Network Adapter - LAN segment (SegA) (NIC - ens33) 192.168.10.1/24
	• Network Adapter 2 - LAN Segment (Segb) (NIC - ens37) 192.168.20.1/24


Metasploit 

	• Network Adapter - LAN segment (SegA) eth0 192.168.10.2/24 - gateway - 192.168.10.1
	
Kali 

	• Network Adapter - Lan Segment (Segb) eth0 192.168.20.2/24 - gateway - 192.168.20.1


